{
  "stem": "1975.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 245.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the reason is, what they did is-- and this was--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, the system that they had, this was applied to each ghetto, which we found out later.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To each-- each ghetto, each camp, that they had, was they used the same-- the same method, same system.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What they wanted to do is actually clean the ghetto from people who were a little bit better educated, you know, so they were not going to have this-- the uprisings or something that is going to affect the-- the-- the-- their grip on the-- on the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we knew that, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that, because there-- there-- Kaunas was surrounded by four forts, a fort.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the forts was the Ninth Fort.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was still some communication between Lithuanians, who used to come to the-- to the-- to the fence.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people used to trade with them, give them, like, a-- a-- a coat or a shirt in exchange for butter or for milk, or for bread, especially.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And many of those people were also without shame.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to take a stone-- butter wrap the stone, and say, that's a kilo butter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, when you found-- when you-- and you had to do that very fast, because apparently the-- the guard should not see that you are trading, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then you find out that you were fooled, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's-- on top of the heavy stones was little bit of butter, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was-- they-- they took all kind of measures in order to fool the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
